headline: Suki Waterhouse, Natasha Lyonne, Devin Booker, Sean Kaufman, Ciara Miller, D-Nice, Kitty Ca$h and More Stun at Target's NYFW Style Tailgate
summary: To celebrate Target's fall collection of trend-first capsule styling must-haves and heritage in democratizing accessible design, Target hosted an unforgettable Target Style Tailgate during New York Fashion Week on Saturday, September 13.
